Rating: 3
Tasty, though I modified the recipe as per many other reviews by adding some honey to the dressing (and some marjoram). Definitely try to seek out a particularly mild blue cheese, otherwise it'll somewhat overpower the rest of the ingredients. All in all, though, a crisp and refreshing salad with good improvisation potential.

