Rating: 4
delicious - i toasted walnuts to top the salad and used a bit of fresh chopped cilantro and majoram plus chopped shallot and some sherry vinegar for the dressing, in addition to lemon juice. i also substituted chopped dates for the currants. the cliantro and walnuts contributed beautifully to the flavors of the apple and fennel.

